text: Jordanoleiopus endroedyi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1972.Biolib.cz - Jordanoleiopus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Polymistoleiopus Category:Beetles described in 1972 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
